data.description: **$7K Seller Credit!** Move in Ready! 5 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, 2 car garage, fenced backyard with no back neighbors.  Downstairs features: Foyer, formal dining room, open kitchen with plenty of cabinet & counter space, island that can accommodate bar stools for an eat-in, spacious living room that offers multiple furniture setup options, a bedroom w/ direct access to a full bathroom.  Upstairs features: Laundry room with shelving above where the washer & dryer go, 3 large bedrooms with great space, oversized primary suite w/ 2 walk-in closets, a full bathroom featuring dual sinks, separate tub & shower, water closet.  Fenced backyard is up against a tree line for some added shade.  The swing-set & picnic table will convey. There's also a neighborhood playground. Close to Shaw AFB & Town.
